{"tid":1545123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"追問警方記者會未回應問題計劃","createTime":"2019-09-05T20:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:47:52.000Z","uid":263731,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1db2156a8aedeab10007c8e2fba86b0076c944a6","tid":1545123,"uid":263731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:55:53.000Z","msg":"又係我。<br />\n<br />\n自從警察一至五日日開記者會之後小弟日日都聽晒，聽左幾日之後就決定整個「追問警方記者會未回應問題計劃」，而家搞左一個月就貼出黎俾大家分享下資料。<br />\n<br />\n我會聽完每日既記者會之後將警察用冇資料、調查緊、了解緊等等理由拒答，或者借啲易答啲唔答啲既問題整理左出黎。基本上都做到最遲翌日深夜更新題目，收到答覆會貼返出黎，不定期會重新檢視有冇問題喺之後記者會答左。<br />\n<br />\n問題列表：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hC3HLCQEjll7wHDp9mB0i6J4R64DDBUMUPd8RN69rWU/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1hC3HLCQEjll7wHDp9mB0i6J4R64DDBUMUPd8RN69rWU%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=7dd7d2a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hC3HLCQEjll7wHDp9mB0i6J4R64DDBUMUPd8RN69rWU/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook Album：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hC3HLCQEjll7wHDp9mB0i6J4R64DDBUMUPd8RN69rWU/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1hC3HLCQEjll7wHDp9mB0i6J4R64DDBUMUPd8RN69rWU%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=7dd7d2a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hC3HLCQEjll7wHDp9mB0i6J4R64DDBUMUPd8RN69rWU/edit#gid=0</a>"},{"pid":"f419e6c8cf151421e3513d6fd5b219bda9c52095","tid":1545123,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:56:02.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail